---
layout: "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
title: "About"
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full bg-black text-white overflow-hidden font-serif">
  <!-- 背景图 -->
  <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Enchanted Forest" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0" />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/70 via-purple-800/40 to-black/90 z-10 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>

  <!-- 星星粒子 -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 pointer-events-none starfield"></div>

  <!-- 正文内容 -->
  <div class="relative z-30 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-40 pb-24 text-center space-y-10">
    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-yellow-100 drop-shadow-glow animate-fade-in">
      Fishnini
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-200 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up">
      You didn’t *arrive* —<br />
      you awakened.<br />
      ✧ A world stitched from stardust and memory. ✧
    </p>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-xl animate-glow-in">
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg italic tracking-wide leading-relaxed">
        “In this forest, forgotten names are whispered back to you by wind and moon.<br />
        You are not lost — you’re home.”
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-14">
      <a href="#top" class="inline-block bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full backdrop-blur-md transition duration-300">
        ⤴ Back to Top
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
@keyframes fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes slide-up {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes glow-in {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.96); filter: blur(2px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); filter: blur(0); }
}

.animate-fade-in { animation: fade-in 1.2s ease-out forwards; }
.animate-slide-up { animation: slide-up 1.4s ease-out forwards; }
.animate-glow-in { animation: glow-in 2s ease-out forwards; }

.starfield {
  background-image: radial-gradient(white 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 20px 20px;
  animation: twinkle 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  opacity: 0.04;
}
@keyframes twinkle {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.02; }
  50% { opacity: 0.08; }
}

.drop-shadow-glow {
  text-shadow: 0 0 12px #facc15, 0 0 24px #f472b6;
}

h1 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
}
p {
  font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
}
</style>

